 🌐 Deployment on Vercel

This project is **live on Vercel** 🚀 — a fast and reliable platform for deploying frontend and full-stack apps.

🔗 || Live Demo ||  [Click Here to View](https://farhaanbaber.vercel.app)  
🟢 **Status:** ✅ Deployed Successfully

🛠️ Steps to Deploy on Vercel:

1. Push your project to ||GitHub||
2. Click || New Project || and import your repository
3. Configure build settings if needed:
   - For frontend-only: No build command needed (static)
   - For backend (like Flask/Node): Set up proper API or build command
4. Click || Deploy ||

✨ That’s it! Vercel will build and host your project automatically, with every GitHub push.

